questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sina Ruppenthal.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;German athlete Sina Ruppenthal achieved a new Guinness World Record during the show &amp;quot;Die gro&amp;szlig;e Show der Weltrekorde&amp;quot; in Munich.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Record:&lt;/strong&gt; She set the record for the fastest time to lift and throw 10 female individuals, completing the task in &lt;strong&gt;37.44 seconds&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Event Location:&lt;/strong&gt; The feat took place in Munich, Germany, and was broadcast on the television channel Sat1.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other Records:&lt;/strong&gt; Ruppenthal is a versatile strength athlete who also holds the record for the fastest strongwoman three obstacle medley.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Motivation:&lt;/strong&gt; She stated her primary goal was to showcase the physical strength and diverse capabilities of women in sports.&lt;/li&gt;
